        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "**Log Sentinel** — Automated operational support for SimSteward.\n\n- **Tier 1** — 7 rule-based detectors run every 60s: error spikes, action failures, WebSocket health, silent sessions, stuck users, incident anomalies, flow gaps.\n- **Tier 2 Fast** — DeepSeek-R1 8B investigates escalated findings (root-cause analysis).\n- **Tier 2 Deep** — Llama 3.3 70B re-investigates low-confidence results.\n\nFindings and investigations are pushed back to Loki as `component=log-sentinel` events.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
